475
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:11,030
Mundy, Kiel...

476
00:40:11,650 --> 00:40:12,650
Volkov.

477
00:40:13,740 --> 00:40:15,910
Chúa ơi, Volkov.

478
00:40:18,740 --> 00:40:19,870
